title: Art Institute of Chicago Palette Key Chain
description:
Keychain developed with our current logo, designed in 2008 by Abbott Miller, partner of Pentagram.

A palette shaped key chain made of metal with colorful enamel paint splashes upon it. On the back is our logo, designed in 2008 by Abbott Miller, partner of Pentagram.

  • Dimensions: 1.85 x 1.36 in.
  • Materials: Metal with chromed finish.
